2005-03-18  Tim Jenness  <timj@jach.hawaii.edu>

	* surflib/surflib_get_focal_station.f (SURFLIB_GET_FOCAL_STATION):
	Create new routine for determing the focal station of the instrument.

	* surflib/surflib_plot_grid.f (SURFLIB_PLOT_GRID): Use KAPLIBS for
	plotting.

	* src/surf_grid_despike.f (SURF_GRID_DESPIKE): Use KAPLIBS for
	plotting (if requested).

