	using strict...

2001-03-01  Tim Jenness  <timj@jach.hawaii.edu>

	* scripts/sculog: Add support for raster skydips

	* sculib/sculib_skydip_temperatures.F
	(SCULIB_SKYDIP_TEMPERATURES): Do not want to special-case when the
	voltage is 0.0 since zero voltage has no special meaning. This is
	the reason for the dropped-skydip-point phenomenon.

