1999-07-14  Tim Jenness  <timj@jach.hawaii.edu>

	* src/surf_rebin.f (SURF_REBIN):  Pass LAT_OBS into
	SCULIB_CALC_APPARENT. 

	* src/surf_read_rebin_ndf.f (SURF_READ_REBIN_NDF): Pass LAT_OBS
	into SCULIB_CALC_APPARENT. 

