	Pass LAT_OBS into SCULIB_CALC_APPARENT and take it as an input
	argument.

	* src/surf_remip.f (SURF_REMIP): Pass LAT_OBS into
	SCULIB_CALC_APPARENT.

	* src/surf_extinction.f (SURF_EXTINCTION): Pass LAT_OBS into
	SCULIB_CALC_APPARENT.

