	to SURFLIB_2DFT_CHOP.

	* surflib_2dft_chop.f (SURFLIB_2DFT_CHOP): Replace IDIMS with NX
	and NY since Linux (g77) can not handle  arrays that control
	dimensions of other arrays. 

